        {
          "data": {
            "content": {
              "segments": [
                {
                  "text": "after transcribing the entire file, I realized that pʊʃ and",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "continuation"
                },
                {
                  "text": "similar sounding things might mean \"open this .\" Things that sound",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "continuation"
                },
                {
                  "text": "like əˈmaɪ or ʊˈmaɪ seem to connote desire roughly, \"I want",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "continuation"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Mommy to\" or \"I want you to\" or something like that: this is what",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "continuation"
                },
                {
                  "text": "CHI usually says when he's asking his mom to do something for him .",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "continuation"
                },
                {
                  "text": "I've transcribed it as \"Mommy\" .",
                  "type": "text"
